{"tid":571664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狼師猥褻女學生　約定成績未達標「任他摸」","createTime":"2018-02-25T00:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T10:01:02.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de0b32677ab099a1cb3c5425af9eb6d02e86830e","tid":571664,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:44:42.000Z","msg":"一名國中教師與女學生約定，若成績未達標準，要讓他摸身體，結果猥褻她40分鐘。被害人導師發現報警，校方將他解聘，台中高分院依妨害性自主罪將他判刑2年10月。<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，判決指出，這名男老師2015年12月20日下午，在辦公室內隔著衣服撫摸女學生胸部。男教師與女學生約定，她成績未達一定標準，他就能任意撫摸她身體；結果女學生成績未達標，他竟撫摸她的身體40分鐘。同月27日，再駕車載她去親戚家猥褻。<br />\n女學生疑惑不安，向同學透露，班導師獲悉後，報警查獲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180225/1303571/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180225%2F1303571%2F&d=DVWoahwgonv%2FIpZBhWpyBzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=07e8b362\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180225%2F1303571%2F&h=c7bbef9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180225/1303571/</a><br />\n<br />\n反正坐...."},{"pid":"6f320a5485b68c9ad2ac43c0846345ab64a2e74c","tid":571664,"uid":78622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"983929ce50a51981f38bc5008bd29795a289f872","tid":571664,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"Goal!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"014bf1aad3ae46fd01fce7f2b7c1cc705f0db796","tid":571664,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f320a5485b68c9ad2ac43c0846345ab64a2e74c","tid":571664,"uid":78622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"所"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"以"},{"pid":"f0d3be355116569586ee68665800a14324dbb389","tid":571664,"uid":48112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱先見到香港完一分 咁快又比台仔追返<img src=\"